What is the space complexity of following recursive code ?

def multiplyRec(m, n):
    if n==1:
        return m
    return m + multiplyRec(m,  n - 1)

ANS: O(n)

=============================================
Problem statement
The space complexity for merge sort is :

ANS: O(n)

=============================================
Problem statement
The space complexity for finding nth fibonacci number using recursion is :

ANS: O(n)

